1
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,680
Miss, are you okay?

2
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,200
Will that guy make a big deal out of this?

3
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,060
Why isn't he answering the phone?

4
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:11,720
Here, drink some water.

5
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:12,880
Don't die of thirst here.

6
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,340
We don't want any trouble.

7
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,880
I'm begging you.

8
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,690
Please let me go.

9
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,380
I don't have any money.

10
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,900
My grandmother is still in the hospital.

11
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,400
I need to take care of her.

12
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,560
We are not extorting you.

13
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,040
Tell me,

14
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,200
will Mu Qingyun come to save you?

15
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,540
Mu Qingyun is still young.

16
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,810
He's just immature.

17
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:34,800
Let me go.

18
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,120
When I get back,

19
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,040
I'll find a time

20
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:40,340
for him to apologize to you in person.

21
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,040
Okay?

22
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,520
No need to make an appointment.

23
00:02:42,520 --> 00:02:43,850
He's already on his way.

24
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,680
What on earth do you want?

25
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,200
What are you doing?

26
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:50,240
Actually, I haven't quite decided.

27
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,890
Just looking for a way to vent my anger.

28
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,680
I'm begging you.

29
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,880
Please don't hurt Mutou.

30
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,960
Don't hurt Mutou.

31
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,040
You're quite a loyal little girl.

32
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,440
What do you want?

33
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:08,120
What good does hurting him do for you?

34
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,920
Watching him suffer

35
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,600
makes me happy.

36
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,210
That's the benefit.

37
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,360
Bring her up.

38
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,880
What are you doing?

39
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,840
Let me go!

40
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:25,040
Mutou, please don't come!

41
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:47,040
What a big scene.

42
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,960
Yuanbao, are you okay?

43
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,880
Mutou, I'm fine. Just go!

44
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,480
Why are you all just standing there?

45
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,930
Are you a girl group?

46
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,440
Cut the crap. Spit it out.

47
00:04:01,160 --> 00:04:01,920
Attack!

48
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,520
Mutou!

49
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,960
Mutou!

50
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,640
Come here.

51
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,360
Grab her.

52
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,760
Mutou!

53
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,079
Yuanbao, I'm fine.

54
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,880
Let him go!

55
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:24,880
Mutou!

56
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,960
Mutou!

57
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,000
Mutou!

58
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,440
I'm fine.

59
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,120
Stop hitting him!

60
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,400
Mutou!

61
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,960
Don't hit him!

62
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,840
Mutou!

63
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:40,520
Mutou!

64
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:41,760
Run!

65
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,560
Mutou!

66
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,480
Mutou, how are you?

67
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,440
Not a big deal.

68
00:04:58,760 --> 00:04:59,400
Mutou!

69
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,360
Mutou!

70
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,120
Mutou!

71
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,360
Yuanbao,

72
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:06,330
don't be afraid.

73
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,130
I'm here to save you.

74
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,840
Since then,

75
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,160
even today, many years later,

76
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,720
I can't recall

77
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,840
the exact details of this incident.

78
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,000
I only remember

79
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,760
that Yuanbao cried for a very long time that day.

80
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:24,320
When she cried, my heart ached.

81
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,720
So,

82
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,000
I can't let anyone bully her.

83
00:05:29,640 --> 00:05:31,320
Yuanbao, don't cry.

84
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,520
When you cry, it makes me want to cry too.

85
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,720
Mutou.

86
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,840
Mutou.

87
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,159
Don't hit him.

88
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,600
Don't hit him.

89
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:56,040
Yuanbao.

90
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,560
Don't be afraid, child.

91
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,960
Don't be afraid, I'm here.

92
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,320
Everything is fine now.

93
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,000
Auntie,

94
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:05,120
I thought I'd never come back.

95
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,280
You're back.

96
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:09,420
Don't be afraid. Everything is fine.

97
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,720
Mutou.

98
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,770
How is Mutou?

99
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:13,480
Mutou.

100
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,480
Mutou is fine. His life is not in danger.

101
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,120
He is in the next ward.

102
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,000
Your uncle is taking care of him.

103
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:22,040
Uncle is back too?

104
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,360
As soon as he heard the news,

105
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,400
he bought a flight ticket and came back immediately.

106
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,040
Mr. Tian also just left.

107
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,320
It's alright.

108
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,880
You're back.

109
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:34,000
Then how long have I been sleeping?

110
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:36,400
You've been sleeping for two or three days.

111
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:39,620
The doctor said you were overly frightened.

112
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:42,080
But the injuries on your body are not a big problem.

113
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,680
But you still need to rest well

114
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,010
to recover your spirit.

115
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,760
Then what about Grandma?

116
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,600
Grandma hasn't recovered yet.

117
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,560
Does Grandma know?

118
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,240
Alright, don't worry.

119
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:54,240
We didn't tell Grandma.

120
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,320
We just told her

121
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:59,360
you and Qingyun went to Shanghai for a competition.

122
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:02,280
So don't show up in front of her these few days

123
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,900
lest she gets suspicious.

124
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,000
Then what about Mutou?

125
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,000
Don't worry. Your uncle is there.

126
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,280
Right, the police will come in a while

127
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,680
to take your statement.

128
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,000
Tell me,

129
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,880
what exactly happened?

130
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:18,840
The police?

131
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:19,640
Yes.

132
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,260
Those guys have been arrested by the police.

133
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:26,760
Well?

134
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,440
Have you made up your mind?

135
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,120
Don't worry.

136
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:31,480
I'll give you the other half of the money after the job is done.

137
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,120
What kind of results do you want?

138
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:36,520
Different results come at different prices.

139
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,880
I don't want you to hit her.

140
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,650
Just warn her and scare her.

141
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,760
Just a little scare.

142
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:45,840
What? You can't even do that?

143
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,280
She's just a little girl.

144
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:49,140
What's so hard about scaring her?

145
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:51,920
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

146
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,260
What do you have to say about this?

147
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,000
Class.

148
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,480
Recently, there has been a

149
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:09,020
very serious vicious incident in our class.

150
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,680
The school has issued an order

151
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,080
for us to take this as a warning

152
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,760
and prevent it from happening again.

153
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:14,520
Therefore,

154
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:17,240
the theme of our class meeting is

155
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,720
preventing school bullying.

156
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:39,840
Yuanbao, why are you here?

157
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,500
Why didn't you rest well in your ward?

158
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,440
I'm fine.

159
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,080
Uncle,

160
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,160
how is Mutou?

161
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:51,760
The doctor said fortunately the wound on his head isn't deep,

162
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:54,040
but his arm took a heavy blow

163
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,040
and fractured.

164
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,960
He'll need a long time to rest

165
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,200
for it to heal slowly.

166
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:04,680
I've already asked for leave for both of you at school.

167
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,720
Just focus on recovering your health,

168
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,780
and don't worry about anything else.

169
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,200
It's all my fault.

170
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,120
I shouldn't have gone abroad

171
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,520
and been so far from home.

172
00:10:18,920 --> 00:10:21,040
I didn't take good care of you.

173
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,080
Uncle,

174
00:10:22,680 --> 00:10:23,920
don't say that.

175
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:27,000
How can you be blamed for this?

176
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,340
Now that Uncle is back,

177
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:29,680
I won't leave.

178
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,940
I'll take good care of you at home.

179
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,480
Money isn't important.

180
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
What's important

181
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:40,280
is that you are safe and healthy.

182
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:45,320
Hello.

183
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:46,600
I came to the hospital today

184
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:48,460
specifically to see the two kids.

185
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,560
This is a small token of my appreciation.

186
00:10:55,560 --> 00:10:56,600
Please accept it.

187
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:01,240
It's just a little money for fruit.

188
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,440
Please don't refuse.

189
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:03,840
What do you mean?

190
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,280
Do you think money makes you so great?

191
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,360
Like mother, like daughter.

192
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,720
With your filthy money,

193
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,600
you can do whatever you want, right?

194
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:13,640
I'm telling you, this isn't over.

195
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:15,640
Your child is already 17 or 18 years old.

196
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,320
After so many years of schooling,

197
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,920
living in a family with such good material conditions,

198
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:21,240
how do you educate her?

199
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:24,280
Doesn't she even know the most basic principles of being a person?

200
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:25,080
Yes.

201
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,010
I've been too busy with work

202
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,720
and neglected Xinrui's discipline.

203
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,640
I never expected

204
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,200
that after she reached puberty,

205
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,600
she would be so rebellious

206
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,060
and dare to do such a thing.

207
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,120
Puberty?

208
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,000
There are many kids in puberty.

209
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,240
Our Yuanbao and Qingjun are both in puberty.

210
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,280
Why didn't they do

211
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,800
such illegal things?

212
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,850
Don't use puberty as an excuse.

213
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:46,080
What? Am I wrong?

214
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,500
About this matter,

215
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,160
I have already learned about it from the police.

216
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,080
Our children

217
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,840
really have no problems.

218
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,000
As for your daughter,

219
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,600
why she would do such a thing,

220
00:11:58,880 --> 00:12:01,120
I heard it's because Yuanbao last time

221
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,720
beat her in the school cheerleading competition,

222
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:06,160
and also because Yuanbao and Meng Jingu,

223
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,480
that is,

224
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,760
Yuanbao's desk mate, became closer,

225
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:10,920
she felt uncomfortable,

226
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,720
which led to this incident.

227
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,800
We are all parents.

228
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,160
We feel sorry for our children.

229
00:12:16,160 --> 00:12:17,960
We can all understand this.

230
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:20,320
But feeling sorry for her is one thing.

231
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,580
Education is another.

232
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,080
The child has made a mistake now.

233
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,240
If you don't let her take responsibility,

234
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,600
it might not be a good thing for her.

235
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:32,690
Our child suffered such severe injuries.

236
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,360
Qingyun is still in a coma,

237
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,770
and she might even have some lasting effects.

238
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,560
As parents,

239
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:42,080
we didn't take good care of our child,

240
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,960
and we already blame ourselves enough.

241
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,960
If we choose to settle for money,

242
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:47,080
then we,

243
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:48,890
we don't deserve to be parents.

244
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:54,400
So, please don't mention the settlement again.

245
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:57,320
Let's just follow the normal procedures, okay?

246
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,080
The court and the police will judge

247
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,740
according to their own rules.

248
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:03,680
If you have time, you should think about

249
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,800
how to properly

250
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:06,720
educate your child in the future.

251
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,860
I understand what you're saying.

252
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:11,320
But Xinrui is only seventeen.

253
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,480
If this happens,

254
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,140
her whole life will be ruined.

255
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:18,290
I know you don't lack money,

256
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:21,180
but right now, money is the only way to make up for it.

257
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:23,720
I can't do anything else.

258
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:25,280
I beg you both,

259
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,480
for the sake of me being a mother too,

260
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,460
please understand me.

261
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:31,920
Please give my daughter another chance.

262
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:32,920
I understand you.

263
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,520
Can you understand me?

264
00:13:36,160 --> 00:13:37,480
If the one lying on the hospital bed right now

265
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,760
were your child?

266
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,880
Let me tell you.

267
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,880
The fact that I didn't treat your child

268
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,680
the same way is already very understanding of you.

269
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:50,560
Whose child isn't the apple of their mother's eye?

270
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,240
If your child

271
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,000
were beaten like this,

272
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,420
how would you feel?

273
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,410
Chairman, what's this?

274
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,290
Are you alright?

275
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,620
Don't be like this.

276
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,200
I don't buy it.

277
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:58,540
Bao, you're awake.

278
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:02,400
I'll go home for a bit later

279
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,520
to get some clothes for your uncle.

280
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,560
He hasn't changed clothes for days.

281
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,480
Be good and stay here.

282
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,240
If anything happens,

283
00:15:11,240 --> 00:15:13,120
call me, okay?

284
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,690
Have some water.

285
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,360
Auntie.

286
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,680
Thank you for your hard work.

287
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,640
It's nothing.

288
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,200
Both of you

289
00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,400
are our darlings.

290
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:29,760
I'll be right back.

291
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,360
Yuanbao,

292
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:28,210
don't be afraid.

293
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:30,010
I'm here to save you.

294
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:45,840
Uncle.

295
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:46,840
Uncle.

296
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:48,280
Mutou is awake.

297
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:52,300
My son is awake.

298
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,100
My son is awake.

299
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,760
Doctor,

300
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:57,560
my son is awake.

301
00:16:58,240 --> 00:17:01,200
Mutou, I was worried to death.

302
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:02,840
It hurts.

303
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:05,359
You have a fracture.

304
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,460
The doctor said you need to rest well.

305
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:11,000
Yuanbao, I'm fine.

306
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,760
I'm tough.

307
00:17:13,839 --> 00:17:15,560
I'll be better in a while.

308
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,319
You want to change seats.

309
00:17:29,920 --> 00:17:32,050
I want to switch seats with Mu Qingjun.

310
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,040
Okay.

311
00:17:34,560 --> 00:17:36,620
Tell me if you need anything anytime.

312
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,440
Thank you, Ms. Tian. I will.

313
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:42,400
I'll go back and switch seats now.

314
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:51,240
Xinrui's mom.

315
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,000
Jingu's mom and I

316
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,480
just heard about this.

317
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:58,520
I didn't expect Xinrui to be so impulsive.

318
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:01,080
It's my fault for being too busy with work

319
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:03,010
and neglecting to discipline her.

320
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:05,600
Don't blame yourself. It's our fault.

321
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,480
Since Xinrui came back,

322
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:08,920
we should have let her stay here.

323
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,480
We didn't do our best.

324
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,020
Please don't say that.

325
00:18:12,840 --> 00:18:13,960
You care about her

326
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:16,160
even more than I do as her mother.

327
00:18:16,760 --> 00:18:19,600
I've always been very grateful to you.

328
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,120
Not at all.

329
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:23,200
Actually, I'm here today

330
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:27,680
to ask Jingu for a favor.

331
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,280
What are you talking about?

332
00:18:31,280 --> 00:18:33,410
He's just a kid. There's no need to ask.

333
00:18:33,440 --> 00:18:35,120
Just tell us what you need.

334
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,680
It's like this.

335
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:38,640
Today,

336
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:40,730
I went to see the victims' parents.

337
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,960
I intended to settle it financially

338
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:45,040
and then transfer Xinrui to another school.

339
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:46,800
But they were too stubborn.

340
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,860
I said all the good things I could,

341
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:51,840
but they just wouldn't agree to settle.

342
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,120
Of course,

343
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,450
I can understand how they feel.

344
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:57,640
But,

345
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,760
Xinrui is only seventeen.

346
00:19:03,200 --> 00:19:05,080
If we really go through the legal process,

347
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:07,540
she'll carry a stain for the rest of her life.

348
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:08,800
Jingu,

349
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,090
you and Xinrui grew up together

350
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,840
like siblings.

351
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,740
Even if Xinrui made a mistake,

352
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:18,320
she should be given a chance to turn over a new leaf.

353
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:20,880
Jingu,

354
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,600
Aunt Gu is talking to you.

355
00:19:22,600 --> 00:19:24,060
Why are you keeping quiet?

356
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,000
I heard

357
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:28,740
when Mu Qingjun was sent to the hospital,

358
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:31,960
his head was covered in blood. Is that true?

359
00:19:32,320 --> 00:19:33,640
If he's too seriously injured

360
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,080
and left with sequelae,

361
00:19:35,640 --> 00:19:37,840
what's the point of giving him more money?

362
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:39,480
His life might be ruined.

363
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,120
Do you know

364
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,520
he actually has good grades.

365
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:50,840
I know what you mean.

366
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,980
But think about it,

367
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:56,200
it's not like Xinrui asked those people to beat them.

368
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:58,060
She didn't expect this to happen.

369
00:19:58,320 --> 00:19:59,920
She didn't expect those kids

370
00:20:00,160 --> 00:20:01,760
to actually start fighting.

371
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,400
It is indeed too much.

372
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,040
I know.

373
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:09,740
Saying all this now

374
00:20:09,760 --> 00:20:10,840
is meaningless.

375
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:15,020
But even if Xinrui bears the legal responsibility,

376
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:16,320
those two kids won't

377
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:18,120
get better immediately, right?

378
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:20,460
It's better to accept this compensation

379
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:23,680
as a guarantee for their future.

380
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:26,760
What's the point of telling me this?

381
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:27,600
Jingu,

382
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,960
how could you talk to Aunt Gu like that?

383
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,720
Exactly.

384
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,260
You are unbelievable.

385
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:33,600
Jingu,

386
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,340
can you go to the hospital?

387
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,800
Talk to that kid named Xiong Yuanbao

388
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,760
and get them to agree to a settlement.

389
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,920
I know you can't let go of your pride.

390
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:42,840
But...

391
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,320
I beg you.

392
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:46,840
Please save our Xinrui.

393
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:48,720
Jingu.

394
00:20:48,720 --> 00:20:51,120
You have to understand Aunt Gu's feelings.

395
00:20:51,560 --> 00:20:52,360
It seems

396
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:55,800
I have to ask for this favor, right?

397
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:57,080
Jingu,

398
00:20:57,680 --> 00:20:58,400
you see,

399
00:20:58,800 --> 00:21:00,680
you and that Xiong Yuanbao

400
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:01,800
are desk mates.

401
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,680
You have a good relationship too.

402
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:05,560
It's easier to communicate

403
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:07,160
when people of the same age talk to each other.

404
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:08,080
Besides,

405
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:09,920
you wouldn't just watch

406
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,360
Xinrui get into trouble.

407
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:12,480
Jingu,

408
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,560
go and talk to Xiong Yuanbao.

409
00:21:14,560 --> 00:21:16,200
As long as she agrees to settle,

410
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,460
no matter what conditions she proposes,

411
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,050
I will agree to them.

412
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,000
If their condition is

413
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:24,840
to beat Xinrui the same way,

414
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,240
would you agree too?

415
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,160
You!

416
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:30,120
You brat!

417
00:21:30,280 --> 00:21:31,400
What nonsense are you talking about?

418
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,260
Come back here!

419
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:33,520
Alright.

420
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:35,320
Sit down.

421
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:51,040
How could Xinrui do such a thing?

422
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,640
She used to be such a good kid.

423
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:56,200
I know you're sad,

424
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,560
but...

425
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,360
Mom.

426
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,440
Okay, I'll stop talking.

427
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:10,080
We'll buy this.

428
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:11,920
You know,

429
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,560
your father was firmly against it at first.

430
00:22:15,080 --> 00:22:16,540
He's willing to buy it now,

431
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:18,760
and I think you know why.

432
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,680
Whether you go or not,

433
00:22:20,960 --> 00:22:22,690
whether you help Xinrui or not,

434
00:22:23,120 --> 00:22:24,160
it's up to you.

435
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:29,090
Son, think about it carefully.

436
00:22:59,200 --> 00:22:59,960
Hello,

437
00:23:00,040 --> 00:23:01,120
Auntie.

438
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:02,400
Hello.

439
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:03,320
Qiao Yan,

440
00:23:03,640 --> 00:23:04,240
Monitor,

441
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,640
you are all here.

442
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:07,280
Then you guys...

443
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:09,410
I'll go out and buy you some breakfast.

444
00:23:09,560 --> 00:23:10,360
Goodbye,

445
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:11,000
Auntie.

446
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:11,680
Bye.

447
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:16,900
The kiwis I bought are very sweet.

448
00:23:19,240 --> 00:23:21,120
Mr. Tian said you two are much better,

449
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:23,560
so we can send representatives to visit you.

450
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:25,440
We couldn't wait to come over.

451
00:23:27,480 --> 00:23:28,960
You have no idea.

452
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:32,360
We were worried sick during this time.

453
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,840
Yeah, worried sick.

454
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,920
By the way, Mutou woke up last night.

455
00:23:36,280 --> 00:23:38,560
Let's quietly go and give him a surprise, okay?

456
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,160
Okay.

457
00:23:39,160 --> 00:23:40,680
Then I'll bring some flowers for Qingyun.

458
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:41,240
Let's go.

459
00:23:41,320 --> 00:23:42,080
Are you okay?

460
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,080
I'm fine.

461
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,200
Slow down, Yuanbao.

462
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:46,330
I'm perfectly fine.

463
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,660
Yuanbao, you're here.

464
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:57,340
To give you a surprise.

465
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:58,680
Surprise!

466
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:01,160
Brother Qingyun, we are here.

467
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:01,720
Surprise!

468
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,520
How is it? Are you surprised?

469
00:24:03,560 --> 00:24:04,600
Are you excited?

470
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,240
Did you miss us?

471
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:08,640
Guys, you're all here.

472
00:24:08,840 --> 00:24:10,200
Bought you some fruits.

473
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:12,000
I put them all in Yuanbao's room.

474
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,730
Wishing you a speedy recovery.

475
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:14,920
Qingyun,

476
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,680
I hope you bounce back soon.

477
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,500
Qingyun, wish you a speedy recovery.

478
00:24:20,800 --> 00:24:23,330
May you eat all you want and never gain weight.

479
00:24:24,840 --> 00:24:26,000
I'm fine.

480
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:28,680
I just can't pick my nose.

481
00:24:29,240 --> 00:24:30,720
Stop moving.

482
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:31,800
Thank you all.

483
00:24:32,600 --> 00:24:33,720
I'm fine now.

484
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,960
But Mutou is seriously injured.

485
00:24:36,440 --> 00:24:38,080
He can't move his hands.

486
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,520
But the doctor said

487
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:40,800
as long as he rests well,

488
00:24:40,800 --> 00:24:42,000
he will recover soon.

489
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:43,880
How is it, Qingyun?

490
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,760
You're the top guy at Zhicheng.

491
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:47,080
Our lineup today

492
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:49,500
is pretty good, right?

493
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:52,080
Thank you, everyone. Thank you.

494
00:24:53,320 --> 00:24:55,320
Don't move. You can talk to them.

495
00:24:55,840 --> 00:24:58,080
By the way, let me tell you some news.

496
00:24:58,920 --> 00:25:01,440
Yesterday, wasn't I called to Mr. Men's office

497
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:03,520
for a heart-to-heart talk?

498
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:06,880
I heard Mr. Men talking with other teachers.

499
00:25:07,080 --> 00:25:08,160
Guess what they were talking about.

500
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:11,280
Were they saying you don't need to go to college,

501
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:14,040
and just inherit your father's fortune-telling stall?

502
00:25:14,040 --> 00:25:15,200
Nice one, Yuanbao.

503
00:25:15,560 --> 00:25:17,890
Yuanbao, has your head not recovered yet?

504
00:25:18,840 --> 00:25:19,800
Mr. Men said

505
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:22,240
before the end of this semester,

506
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:24,920
he plans to take us on a field trip.

507
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,080
Really?

508
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,920
Then we can all go have fun together.

509
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:30,680
Yes.

510
00:25:33,440 --> 00:25:34,560
Can I go too?

511
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:39,520
Hero Gong Yu.

512
00:25:39,560 --> 00:25:40,640
Hero.

513
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:42,240
Are you staying in this hospital too?

514
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:43,680
I heard Mu Qingjun is awake.

515
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:45,280
Can I move in to stay with you?

516
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:47,320
No problem.

517
00:25:47,600 --> 00:25:49,400
There's an empty bed right here.

518
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:50,440
Whatever.

519
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:51,760
Come, let me help you.

520
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,520
Let me help.

521
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:53,320
Careful, careful.

522
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:53,920
Slow down.

523
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:55,160
Slow down, hero.

524
00:25:56,040 --> 00:25:57,080
Come, slow down.

525
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,660
Your injury is quite serious.

526
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,320
Slow down, slow down.

527
00:26:00,320 --> 00:26:01,000
Hurry.

528
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:02,850
Slow down, slow down. Come.

529
00:26:03,240 --> 00:26:04,480
You must be Yuanbao.

530
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:07,000
Yes.

531
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:08,560
Okay, okay, that's fine.

532
00:26:08,760 --> 00:26:10,160
You classmates chat.

533
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,800
I'll go pack some things for Xiaoyu.

534
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:13,880
Okay, okay.

535
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:14,680
You guys chat.

536
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:15,600
Bye, Grandpa.

537
00:26:15,600 --> 00:26:16,240
Goodbye, Grandpa.

538
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:17,240
Goodbye, goodbye.

539
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,360
Not bad.

540
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:20,840
The two heroes are sharing a room.

541
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,760
It's gonna be lively.

542
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,600
Well, when we go on the outing together,

543
00:26:25,600 --> 00:26:27,600
I plan to wear my most handsome clothes,

544
00:26:27,600 --> 00:26:30,960
and then give you guys a Chris Lee concert.

545
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:34,320
I only have you in my heart, not him.

546
00:26:34,360 --> 00:26:37,120
You must believe my affection is not fake.

547
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,240
Shang Ningyu,

548
00:26:38,280 --> 00:26:39,280
I think you can

549
00:26:39,320 --> 00:26:40,720
add another bed here.

550
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:47,460
Your singing makes me feel like my condition is getting worse.

551
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:50,580
You girls don't laugh either.

552
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,160
Can you guys dress up a bit?

553
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:53,920
Don't act like a dude all day.

554
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:54,800
Shang Ningyu,

555
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:56,720
watch your words.

556
00:26:56,880 --> 00:26:58,200
Be careful,

557
00:26:58,760 --> 00:27:00,160
or Yuanbao will bite you.

558
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:03,480
Well.

559
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:05,120
Let's take a group photo,

560
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:06,640
since everyone is fine.

561
00:27:07,440 --> 00:27:07,770
Sure.

562
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:08,560
Sure, sure.

563
00:27:08,600 --> 00:27:09,040
Sure.

564
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,120
Come on, let's take a photo.

565
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:12,720
Your brother looks like a mess and you still want a photo?

566
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:14,000
Come on, bro, let's take one.

567
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,440
I'll count 3, 2, 1, and everyone say cheese.

568
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:21,360
Cheese.

569
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,120
Take one more.

570
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:26,450
Let me tell you, Gong Yu.

571
00:27:37,520 --> 00:27:38,400
What's wrong?

572
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:40,960
Well,

573
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:41,840
bros,

574
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,760
we'll visit you again when we're free.

575
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:46,360
We'll head out first.

576
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:46,800
Yeah,

577
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:47,860
we're heading out.

578
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,120
Bye, Qingyun.

579
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:49,960
Let's go.

580
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:51,800
Let's go.

581
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,400
Bye.

582
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,320
How are you feeling?

583
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:25,320
Much better.

584
00:28:27,040 --> 00:28:28,900
I didn't know what you like to eat,

585
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,360
so I just bought whatever.

586
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:31,120
Thank you.

587
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,850
You really shouldn't have.

588
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:35,320
Qingyun, about this time,

589
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,520
I am really sorry.

590
00:28:38,280 --> 00:28:39,410
It's not your fault.

591
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,900
Let's go outside and talk.

592
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:42,940
Let's not disturb their rest.

593
00:29:10,280 --> 00:29:11,320
I am really sorry.

594
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:17,320
Actually, you don't have to apologize.

595
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:18,480
I...

596
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,570
I'm sorry for what happened to you.

597
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:25,300
Don't blame yourself.

598
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,440
This time,

599
00:29:30,120 --> 00:29:31,040
I am not just

600
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,760
apologizing for myself.

601
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,880
You're here to apologize for Gu Xinrui.

602
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:49,890
If you are here to apologize for Gu Xinrui,

603
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:52,580
then it's even more unnecessary.

604
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:54,970
You weren't the one who sent those people.

605
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:57,120
The culprit hasn't even apologized,

606
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:58,480
so why should you?

607
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,320
Go back.

608
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:02,640
Class is about to start.

609
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,320
Yuanbao,

610
00:30:04,200 --> 00:30:04,920
I know

611
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,360
this is too much to ask,

612
00:30:08,760 --> 00:30:10,690
but her family has been begging me.

613
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:13,360
Can you give her another chance?

614
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:15,080
If you take legal action,

615
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:17,040
her life might be ruined.

616
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,200
Meng Jingu,

617
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:20,920
if you came here today

618
00:30:21,120 --> 00:30:22,840
with a sincere apology,

619
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:25,600
I appreciate it.

620
00:30:28,080 --> 00:30:29,200
But if you came today

621
00:30:29,200 --> 00:30:30,560
to plead for Gu Xinrui,

622
00:30:31,280 --> 00:30:32,280
you should leave.

623
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:33,690
I'm not that forgiving.

624
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,640
Yuanbao,

625
00:30:35,760 --> 00:30:36,480
I'm sorry.

626
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,160
I know you're angry,

627
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,640
but I have my reasons.

628
00:30:40,960 --> 00:30:42,040
Can you tell me

629
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:44,520
what they can do

630
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,640
to make it up to you?

631
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:51,000
Angry?

632
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,920
Is it just about being angry?

633
00:30:55,080 --> 00:30:56,400
Do you know what

634
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:57,920
we went through that day?

635
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,440
Do you know

636
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,640
how fragile human bones are?

637
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:05,520
One hit with a stick

638
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,840
can break them.

639
00:31:11,240 --> 00:31:12,520
Do you know that the blood

640
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,780
flowing out of the body

641
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:14,800
is hot

642
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,080
and sticky?

643
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,600
Do you know what despair is?

644
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:24,120
You said Gu Xinrui's life would be ruined.

645
00:31:26,040 --> 00:31:27,040
When she gets out,

646
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:29,050
she can just go back to the UK

647
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:31,040
and continue being a rich girl.

648
00:31:31,560 --> 00:31:32,760
But what about Mutou?

649
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,000
You saw him just now.

650
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:39,000
What if he suffers from lingering effects?

651
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:41,080
What if he gets disabled?

652
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,800
Who exactly harmed whom?

653
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,840
Tell me!
